<font color="#FF0000">JUST BECAUSE WE COULD</font><br>
<tt>Sun Dec 14 19:56:39 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I remember flying over the chaos with the most powerful radios of the theater on board.  When the conditions were right we would hook up to a sight in New Jersey and offer phone patches home.  Reach out and touch someone just because we could.  I am sure some still aren't sure how they talked to their loves ones over their radios.<br><br>
We never told them what was happening because it wasn't supposed to be.
<p><code>--   (SW) </code><p>


